   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>snapshot 2010-11-12.json.gz
table: profile_person
field: contact_blurb
id=46
above field contains emailaddress

Suggestion:
When a snapshot is made: regex on emaikadresses on fields and replace or delete
them. Process will be expensive in CPU, disk IO and time but will guarantee
removal of email-addresses even in fields not supposed to contain them.</pre>
